WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.390 --> 00:00:03.760
Previously on <i>Teen Wolf</i>

2
00:00:03.890 --> 00:00:05.960
Lydia. run!

3
00:00:06.090 --> 00:00:09.260
<font color="#3A9583">Sync by YYeTs</font>
